"创建或覆盖一个 AI 可复用的 JavaScriptCore（JSC）自定义工具。脚本会保存到应用 Application Support 下的 CustomJSTools 独立目录，每个工具包含 manifest.json 与 script.js。脚本必须声明同步 function main(input)，创建前会用 validation_input 试运行；如果工具需要参数，请提供一份能通过校验的 validation_input，否则验证失败不会保存。以后会以 app_custom_jsc_<tool_id> 暴露给模型。能力边界：没有 Node.js、文件系统、原生网络 API 或 Promise 返回值能力。" = "Create or overwrite an AI-reusable JavaScriptCore (JSC) custom tool. The script is saved under the app Application Support CustomJSTools directory; each tool contains manifest.json and script.js. The script must declare synchronous function main(input), and validation_input is used for a test run before creation. If the tool requires parameters, provide validation_input that passes validation; otherwise the tool is not saved. It will later be exposed to the model as app_custom_jsc_<tool_id>. Limits: no Node.js, file system, native network APIs, or Promise return values.";
"创建或覆盖一个 AI 可复用的 watchOS WebKit JavaScript bridge 自定义工具。脚本会保存到应用 Application Support 下的 CustomJSTools 独立目录，每个工具包含 manifest.json 与 script.js。脚本必须声明同步 function main(input)，创建前会用 validation_input 试运行；如果工具需要参数，请提供一份能通过校验的 validation_input，否则验证失败不会保存。以后会以 app_custom_webkit_js_<tool_id> 暴露给模型。能力边界：这是 WebKit JS bridge，不是 JavaScriptCore.framework；没有 Node.js、文件系统、原生网络 API、外部页面 DOM 或 Promise 返回值能力。" = "Create or overwrite an AI-reusable watchOS WebKit JavaScript bridge custom tool. The script is saved under the app Application Support CustomJSTools directory; each tool contains manifest.json and script.js. The script must declare synchronous function main(input), and validation_input is used for a test run before creation. If the tool requires parameters, provide validation_input that passes validation; otherwise the tool is not saved. It will later be exposed to the model as app_custom_webkit_js_<tool_id>. Limits: this is the WebKit JS bridge, not JavaScriptCore.framework; there is no Node.js, file system, native network API, external page DOM, or Promise return value support.";
